# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# In a GitHub Codespace, set these as Codespace Secrets instead.
# Never commit .env to version control — it is gitignored.
# See README.md for instructions on setting up Codespace Secrets.

# ── Project-specific variables ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Add your project's required environment variables below.
# Document each one with a comment explaining what it is and where to get it.

# Example:
# AMERIFLUX_USER_NAME=          # Your registered AmeriFlux account name
# AMERIFLUX_USER_EMAIL=         # Your registered AmeriFlux account email
# AMERIFLUX_INTENDED_USE=1      # 1=Synthesis, 2=Model, 3=Remote sensing, etc.
